column1: # Results of Galfit fitting to the stellar mass projections of EAGLE galaxies at z=0.1
# COLUMN 2	[-]	best-fit integrated stellar mass log(Mstar/Msun) from Galfit
# COLUMN 3	[-]	uncertainty on the best-fit integrated stellar mass log(Mstar/Msun) from Galfit
# COLUMN 4	[kpc]	best-fit semi-major axis from Galfit
# COLUMN 5	[kpc]	uncertainty on the best-fit semi-major axis from Galfit
# COLUMN 6	[-]	best-fit Sersic index from Galfit
# COLUMN 7	[-]	uncertainty on the best-fit Sersic index from Galfit
# COLUMN 8	[-]	best-fit axis ratio from Galfit
# COLUMN 9	[-]	uncertainty on the best-fit axis ratio from Galfit
# COLUMN 10	[deg]	best-fit position angle from Galfit
# COLUMN 11	[deg]	uncertainty on the best-fit position angle from Galfit
# COLUMN 12	[-]	quality flag (see description in Section 3.2.3)
